<section class="px-6 py-section sm:py-section-lg bg-white text-black">
  <div class="section-container text-center">
    <span class="section-eyebrow">PRINCIPLES</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">Our principles</h2>
    <div class="mt-14 grid gap-6 sm:gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">

      <div class="card-light reveal">
        <div class="glyph-light mb-4 mx-auto">*</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-black">
          Open source today,<br>open-weight soon.
          <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium bg-ink-200 text-ink-500 ml-1.5 align-middle">Coming soon</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-ink-700 leading-relaxed">
          The harness and project code are already public. Open-weight models are on the roadmap. No bait-and-switch — community-driven, forever.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card-light reveal" style="transition-delay: 80ms;">
        <div class="glyph-light mb-4 mx-auto">=</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-black">Model-agnostic.</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-ink-700 leading-relaxed">
          Bring your own model, bring your own key. No vendor lock-in, no subscription required.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card-light reveal" style="transition-delay: 160ms;">
        <div class="glyph-light mb-4 mx-auto">~</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-black">Your memory is portable.</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-ink-700 leading-relaxed">
          Export your memory anytime and take it anywhere — never locked to us. Your context, your choice.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
